---

## 1) Product Summary

ViralBoost AI ek creator-focused SaaS platform hai jo video creators, agencies, aur teams ko content planning, analysis, optimization, publishing insights, aur growth strategy me help karta hai.

Main objective:
- better content decisions,
- faster production workflow,
