Also dynamic behavior hardened for server-side data usage routes.

**Cron jobs (middleware):** `/api/cron/daily`, `/api/cron/ai-retrain`, `/api/cron/sync-prediction-outcomes` ŌĆö JWT ke bina call ho sakte hain; har route **andar** `Authorization: Bearer CRON_SECRET` verify karti hai (agar `CRON_SECRET` set ho).

## H. Mobile App (PWA + Native Shell)
- **PWA install:** `public/manifest.webmanifest` + `public/sw.js`, and `components/PWARegister.tsx` registers the service worker for ŌĆ£Add to Home ScreenŌĆØ / standalone feel
- **Native mobile shell (Android):** `mobile/` uses **Capacitor** to wrap the existing website inside a WebView (no separate React Native rewrite). Server URL is controlled by `CAPACITOR_SERVER_URL`
- **Dev/run from terminal:** `npm run mobile:run:android` / `cd mobile && npm run run:android` (uses `cap run android`); Android Studio Snap JBR is auto-detected for Gradle

## I. Production AI, Queue, Monitoring (add-on stack)
- **Python FastAPI** viral ML service (`ai-services/viral_prediction/`) ŌĆö embeddings + classifier; Node calls it first, **internal ensemble fallback** if down
- **Ground truth / validation (real labels ŌĆö not fake metrics):**
  - Har prediction par `engagement` = **prediction ke waqt ka snapshot** (inputs)
  - **`outcome`** subdocument = **baad me verify** hua asli result: `viralScore0to100`, views/likes/comments, `capturedAt`, `source` (`youtube_api` | `user_submitted` | `admin` | `cron_sync`)
  - **`POST /api/ai/outcome`** ŌĆö user/admin apne prediction par actual stats ya score submit karke label banata hai
  - **`POST /api/cron/sync-prediction-outcomes`** ŌĆö `CRON_SECRET` + YouTube Data API se jin `ViralPrediction` me `videoId` hai aur `outcome` khali hai, un par auto-label (`services/youtubeVideoStats.ts`, `lib/predictionOutcomeSync.ts`)
  - **`GET /api/ai/metrics`** ŌĆö MAE/RMSE **sirf** jahan `outcome.viralScore0to100` set hai; kam labels par `null` + `insufficientGroundTruth`; `?scope=global` sirf super-admin (warna sirf apne predictions)
  - **Training:** Python/ worker training samples me **pehle** `getLabeledPredictionTrainingSamples()` (verified outcomes), phir `ViralDataset` ŌĆö true labels pipeline retrain ke liye
  - Helpers: `lib/viralOutcome.ts` (score formula, YouTube id extract), predict API me `videoId` / `videoUrl` save for sync
- **Super Admin AI Monitoring:** UI `/admin/super/ai-monitoring` + `GET /api/admin/super/ai-monitoring` (models, **labeledPredictions** count, total predictions, support AI, queue)
- **Background jobs:** Redis + **BullMQ** queue (`lib/queue.ts`), worker `workers/aiWorker.ts` ŌĆö optional async **prediction / training / support_ai** when env flags on; `AIJobLog` model
- **Auto-retrain cron hook:** `POST /api/cron/ai-retrain` + scheduler wiring; model **rollback** API for admins
- **Support AI:** OpenAI-based classification/replies (`services/ai/supportAI.ts`), embeddings helper; routes e.g. `/api/support/ai-reply`, enriched `/api/support/tickets`
- **Chat memory:** `ChatSession` / `ChatMessage` ŌĆö `/api/support/chat`, `/api/support/chat/history`
- **Observability hooks:** structured logging (`lib/observability.ts`); Sentry dependency present for errors

User value:
- more reliable AI at scale; admin visibility into model health; optional offload of heavy work to workers

