# ViralBoost AI ŌĆō Website Systems, Kaise Kaam Karta Hai, aur Fayde (Full Detail)

Is file mein website ke saare systems, unka kaam karne ka tareeka, aur users ko kis cheez se kya fayda hota hai ŌĆō sab detail mein diya gaya hai.

---

## 1. WEBSITE KYA HAI AUR KISKE LIYE HAI

**ViralBoost AI** ek SaaS platform hai jisse content creators, YouTubers, aur agencies apne videos ka viral potential analyze kar sakte hain. Ye website:

- Video analysis (YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok, direct upload) karti hai
- Viral score, title suggestions, hashtags, best posting time deti hai
- Trends, competitor analysis, analytics dashboard provide karti hai
- **Free**, **Starter**, **Pro**, **Enterprise** (aur custom) plans ŌĆö **monthly/yearly amounts Super Admin ŌĆ£Manage PlansŌĆØ se**; marketing/signup/checkout sab **same DB prices** follow karte hain (default reference: Starter **~$3/mo**, Pro **~$15/mo** ŌĆö admin change kar sakta hai)

**Fayda:** Creators ko data-driven decisions; pricing ek jagah manage, har page par mismatch nahi.

---

## 2. LOGIN AUR AUTHENTICATION SYSTEM

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- **Do tarah se login:** (1) **Unique ID (6 digit) + PIN** ŌĆō jaldi login ke liye (2) **Email + Password** ŌĆō full account access
- Signup par email verify OTP bhejta hai; OTP verify hone ke baad user banta hai
- Password **Forgot Password** se reset ho sakta hai (link email par aata hai)
- JWT token se session maintain hota hai; sidebar se **Logout** kar sakte hain

### APIs
- `POST /api/auth/login` ŌĆō Email + password login
- `POST /api/auth/login-pin` ŌĆō Unique ID + PIN login
- `POST /api/auth/register` ŌĆō Naya user
- `POST /api/auth/send-otp` ŌĆō OTP bhejna
- `POST /api/auth/verify-otp` ŌĆō OTP verify
- `GET /api/auth/me` ŌĆō Current user details (role, plan, expiry, account manager, etc.)
- `POST /api/auth/password-reset` ŌĆō Reset link request
- `PUT /api/auth/password-reset` ŌĆō Naya password set (token ke sath)

### Fayde
- Secure login; PIN se fast access; password reset se account recover; har user ko apna 6-digit ID milta hai.

