## 4. VIDEO ANALYSIS SYSTEM

### Kaise kaam karta hai
- User video **URL** de sakta hai (YouTube, Facebook, Instagram, TikTok) ya **file upload** kar sakta hai
- Har video par: **hook analysis** (shuruat attract karti hai?), **thumbnail analysis**, **title analysis**, **viral prediction**, **hashtags**, **trending score**, **best posting time** nikala jata hai
- **Title optimization:** Free = 3 suggestions, Pro/Enterprise = 10 suggestions
- **Hashtag generator:** 10ŌĆō20 hashtags (plan ke hisaab)
- Result **Viral Optimizer** page par dikhta hai; copy kar sakte ho
- Analysis DB mein save hota hai; **My Videos** se list dekhi ja sakti hai

### APIs
- `POST /api/videos/youtube` ŌĆō YouTube URL analyze
- `POST /api/videos/facebook` ŌĆō Facebook URL
- `POST /api/videos/instagram` ŌĆō Instagram URL
- `POST /api/videos/tiktok` ŌĆō TikTok URL
- `POST /api/videos/upload` ŌĆō File upload analyze
- `POST /api/videos/bulk-analyze` ŌĆō Ek saath multiple URLs (Pro/Enterprise, max 10)

### Fayde
- Har video ke liye viral score, better titles, hashtags, posting time ŌĆō content zyada engage kare; bulk se time bachta hai.

---

## 5. VIRAL PREDICTION AUR AI

### Kaise kaam karta hai (API: `/api/ai/predict`, `/api/ai/train`, `/api/ai/outcome`)
- Hook, thumbnail, title, text, engagement snapshot se **viral probability** aur **confidence**; body me **`videoId`** ya **`videoUrl`** bhejo taaki baad me YouTube sync se **outcome** bharkar **sahi labels** milen
- **Python FastAPI** service (embeddings + sklearn pipeline) ŌĆö primary; **internal ensemble** fallback
- Training: dataset + **verified predictions** (`outcome` wale rows) merge ho kar Python/ worker train call
- **MAE / RMSE:** `GET /api/ai/metrics` ŌĆö **ground truth only** (`outcome.viralScore0to100`); 5+ labeled samples ke baad hi numbers; super-admin `?scope=global`
- **Feedback loop:** manually `POST /api/ai/outcome` (views/likes/comments ya seedha `viralScore0to100`); cron `POST /api/cron/sync-prediction-outcomes` (YouTube API + `CRON_SECRET`)

### APIs (short)
- `POST /api/ai/predict` ŌĆö save + optional `videoId`/`videoUrl`
- `POST /api/ai/outcome` ŌĆö label ek prediction (owner ya super-admin)
- `GET /api/ai/metrics` ŌĆö labeled-only accuracy; `POST /api/ai/train` ŌĆö Enterprise training (labeled samples pref)

### Fayde
- Model accuracy ab **approx input-vs-input** nahi, **prediction vs verified outcome** se measure hoti hai; retraining ko **true labels** mil sakte hain.

